    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-05-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-05-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="752"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d752">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/11849.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Mediators</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translations.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-05-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 5, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>We have the honor to inform your excellency that upon consulting all the opinions
                    concerned, the city of Niagara Falls, Canada, has been designated as the seat of
                    the conferences at which the bases of settlement for the pacific and friendly
                    solution of the conflict pending between the United States and Mexico will be
                    discussed, and that said conferences will open on the 18th day of the present
                    month at the hour and place that will be named in due time.</p>
                <p>We take pleasure at the same time in informing your excellency that General
                    Huerta’s Government has given us official notice of the appointment of Messrs.
                    Emilio Rabasa, Augustin Rodríguez y Luis Elguero to represent it at the said
                    conferences, and that Señor Rafael Elguero will act as their Secretary.</p>
                <p>We avail [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <list>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">D. da Gama</hi>.</item>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">R. S. Naón</hi>.</item>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Edo. Suarez Mujica</hi>.</item>
                        </list>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
